snippet.title: Otherplane - Announce Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist Otherplane on Steam
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2245610/Otherplane/

Otherplane is a 1-4 player co-op horror game where you solve escape-room like puzzles and evade ghostly entities that become more aggressive as you progress.
